<reg_short_dscr>:
General Status
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Debug information for checking register read/write problems. This is a read-only field which can only be cleared by reset of the VCore System.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0: No errors detected.
1: Non-32bit access to VCore or SwC registers, access has been discarded, read returns 0x8888 or 0x88.
2: SwC registers not ready when accessed, access has been discarded, read returns 0x88888888.
3: SwC registers reported error, check DEVCPU_ORG::ERR_CNTS for error, read returns 0x88888888.
4: Unimplemented VCore register, access has been discarded, read returns 0x88888888.
