<field_public_text>:
Set to enable 32bit address mode. If set 4 bytes of address is sent in address phase, otherwise 3 bytes. 
In 24bit addressing mode CS0 to CS3 is used, the SPI address region is limited to 64MB of the 1GB reserved SI interface.
In 32bit addressing mode CS0 to CS3 is used, the SPI address region is limited to 1GByte reserved for the SI interface.
