------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Controls generation of WAKE signal generation during wake-up from low power modes.
Note: Unused in RC mode of operation of controller
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0:Wake signal generation enabled
1:Wake signal generation disabled.
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Polarity of Wake signal as used in EP & RC modes:
In EP Mode of Controller:
Polarity of the PCIe WAKE output, WAKE is typically an active low output - but if an amplifier is needed for driving a large WAKE net then polarity may need to be changed.
