<reggrp_public_text>:
These are the VCore interrupt controller registers. The controller has 50 interrupt sources (inputs) which can each be mapped to one of 2 interrupt destinations (outputs). The controller has a dedicated block for handling device and serdes interrupts; the handling of these interrupts can be considered as a small interrupt controller located before the interrupt controller.
